3x \equiv 1\ (mod\ 11)
{\rm\ mod}\ 11\!:\ 10\equiv -1\,\Rightarrow\, 10^2\equiv 1\,\Rightarrow\, \color{#c00}{419}\equiv 4\!-\!1\!+\!9\equiv \color{#c00}1,\ \ \color{#0a0}{91}\equiv -9\!+\!1\equiv \color{#0a0}3.\,
\ \color{#0a0}{91}x\equiv \color{#c00}{419}\iff \color{#0a0}3x\equiv \color{#c00}1\ (\equiv 12),\ 
\ x\equiv\, \ldots
